name: YourHealthyTips
0:
”Alexa, open Your Healthy Tips”
”Give me a tip on nutrition”
”Tell me something about exercise”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: your healthy tips
des:
Most weight loss programs combine healthy eating with increased activity to lose excess pounds. Whether as a part of such a weight loss plan or just to improve your fundamental lifestyle behaviors, Your Healthy Tips is a tool to help you adopt healthier habits in nutrition and exercise. Just ask Your Healthy Tips to give you a tip on exercise or nutrition, and it will provide you with a useful suggestion to help you make positive changes. It’s easy and convenient!

For more information and other tools to help you work towards healthy weight loss, visit www.InsightsForHealth.com. Membership is free and, once a member, you can take advantage of its many tools.

The information in this skill or that provided on www.InsightsFrorHealth.com is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment, or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
